===Adjective===
{{en-adj|-}}

# Capable of operating without external [[control]] or [[intervention]].
#: ''The '''automatic''' clothes washer was a great labor-saving device''
# Done out of [[habit]] or without [[conscious]] thought.
#: ''The reaction was '''automatic''': flight!''
# {{context|of a [[firearm]] such as a [[machine gun]]}} Firing continuously as long as the [[trigger]] is pressed until [[ammunition]] is exhausted.
# {{computing|of a local [[variable]]}} Being added and removed from the [[stack]] automatically during the course of [[function]] [[call]]s.

